    <briefdescription>
<para>Wraps a <ref refid="classDali_1_1SignalConnection" kindref="compound">SignalConnection</ref> with emission-order linked list indices. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1BaseSignal" kindref="compound">BaseSignal</ref> maintains an intrusive doubly-linked list of these nodes to guarantee that callbacks fire in connection order. The pool allocates nodes; the linked list determines iteration order during Emit().</para>
<para>Uses uint32_t indices instead of pointers to reduce memory footprint:</para>
<para>@SINCE_2_5.17 </para>
    </detaileddescription>
